<item>
            <title>[SEC-612] Account authentication policy support</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-612</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Listen for authentication success and authentication failure events, and update tables accordingly. Integrate with account locking capabilities. Provide a querying interface to retrieve all events associated with a user after a particular date.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We also might want to consider logging authorizations as well, although that is probably a separate issue. We will certainly need to consider archival issues if we did that.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
